<title>THE GATE AJAR FOR ME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kawtkhak khat kihawngsa a um,
 Zie kawtkhak vak apat chun;
 Gamla taka Kross vak alang,
 Hukdampa hehpih a phuong.

[V2]
 Aw, hehpihna athuk na e!
 Kawt chuh keia di'n hawn ahim?
 Kei di'n .... Kei di'n!
 Kei dingin hawn ahim?

[V3]
 2. Mitin di'n kawt chuh hawn ahi,
 Hukdamna hawlte adi'n;
 Ahau, avai, alien, aneu,
 Namtin, chitinte a di'n.

[V4]
 3. Lungsietna kawt hawn lai ahi,
 Dogal te do ham ham un;
 Hailo in Kross pu zel unla,
 Lallukhuk tiemsa ahi.

[V5]
 4. Zie taka Kross I put u hi,
 Luigal achun nga tai tiu;
 Hinna Lallukhuk khu taiting,
 Amah lungsiet zaw tai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>